responseText: Look around you. Do you see our strength? Too long have the Vaelune people languished in the shadow of the Kaelar empire. On Sanctus, we almost lost ourselves completely, barely clinging to our ancestral remembrance, but here - on Verra? We rise! Mother Vyra has gifted us our birthright, plain to see on our faces! Your time of ascendancy is over, oppressor!
name: SQ_RVR_NPC_Samias_Miraleth_Sabah_19_Response
